{"tid":1411432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"運動無變過質, 而係政府從無落實過五大訴求","createTime":"2019-08-05T03:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:21:24.000Z","uid":37722,"like":116,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d7c1fe1dde279c57763efd0f82c0058eaffdba4e","tid":1411432,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:40:05.000Z","msg":"對家出語言偽術由雨革開始已經做緊, 要應對其實好簡單: <span style=\"color: red;\">將所有問題轉移返去政府責任, 同埋加強己方係事態上既被動性</span>. 下面做少少例子黎回應下林鄭出既語言偽術, 比文宣同所有人參考下<br />\n<br />\n<strong>- 運動變質</strong><br />\n1. 場運動既目的就係要政府落實五大訴求 (唔好再講&quot;回應&quot;, 比對方出語言偽術), 一日政府唔落實五大訴求, 抗爭者用咩方式, 咩方法都無變過質<br />\n2. 對方話係變質, 事實上場<span style=\"color: red;\">運動係發掘出香港其他更深層次既問題</span>, 警狗如同黑社會, 濫用暴力, 市民申訴無路, 警黑勾結, 所有問題唔係因為呢場運動而出現, 而係根深柢固. 場運動既最終目的就係要<span style=\"color: red;\">正視香港所有根本問題</span>, 只要政府一日唔落實五大訴求, 運動一日都無變過質<br />\n<br />\n<strong>- 經濟影響</strong><br />\n1. 經濟受影響係<span style=\"color: red;\">因為政府施政失敗之餘仍然態度強硬, 絲毫無落實過市民最基本訴求, 令投資者對香港政府既管治嚴重失去信心</span>而造成, 抗爭者只不過係港共政府失敗既受害者<br />\n2. 政府要解決經濟影響既問題, <span style=\"color: red;\">最直接既方式係立即落實五大訴求, 等投資者知道政府為民而治, 重拾投資信心</span>, 但政府寧願冷處理, 加長經濟受衝擊既時間, 所以所有問題既根源都係政府身上<br />\n<br />\n另外, 致各位記者朋友, 對方出語言偽術已經唔係第一次, 我地而家手上仲要一手好牌, <span style=\"color: red;\">問問題/應對政府就更加要拎主導權, 而唔係比人舞</span>. 林鄭如果話運動變質/已回應條例問題, 我地就應該轉陣地, 屌佢黑警問題點解從來無解決. 林鄭話警隊盡忠職守, 我地就係反向屌佢無落實過五大訴求令事件升溫, 仲要拎黑狗濫權黎補刀."},{"pid":"f09772cb2fdf8368c0cf2dddfdbc9adb969f5dd3","tid":1411432,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d997ac485394a7f90af99e28ae8853a2e58d32cd","tid":1411432,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:42:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d819717bac6acae1408d6084ea63a63c063a2a90","tid":1411432,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:45:17.000Z","msg":"人手置頂"},{"pid":"7dde55f80b732eb02a70d289db710092cc750e2c","tid":1411432,"uid":74063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5056a0be77dcb393755554f8bbbb1f870a3485d5","tid":1411432,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58cfee694e1c41684f6c7a43ff00bd7800b09e87","tid":1411432,"uid":113399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:46:03.000Z","msg":"制裁黑警! 撒回惡法!"},{"pid":"b956384481307befb992a7bf57349e626baf4d28","tid":1411432,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53846f5414d45978434f3f299cd300f78d872f1b","tid":1411432,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c844883ff126f8228e5fb0b9ce45bf37b3aa6ea6","tid":1411432,"uid":1327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:47:06.000Z","msg":"岩 pushhhh"},{"pid":"56ce21d693097c3a9309a335b82a0d5ad73ce2ea","tid":1411432,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:47:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ed4fd2a1ff08f3f9989ee77082c38cc9a200ec","tid":1411432,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:48:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed03aad